      "rationale": "Formal use error assessment not required at MRL 2. CFD analyses performed by analysts with documented competency in rotary blood pump simulation. Simulation setup reviewed by independent senior analyst prior to result acceptance."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
