      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties) must be traceable to measurement data or manufacturer specifications with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Pump geometry derived from manufacturer CAD files with dimensional inspection report confirming agreement within 0.05 mm. Inlet boundary conditions (flow rate, rotational speed) set from experimental test rig measurements. Blood analog viscosity characterised by rheometry. Input uncertainty documented in model input register."
